text: Kaitlyn Ashley Maher (born January 10, 2004) is an American singer and actress, best known for being the Youngest Top 10 Finalist on America's Got Talent and for her roles in movies, such as The Search for Santa Paws, Santa Paws 2, Free Birds, and the PupStar series. Maher was born in Novi, Michigan and currently lives in Ashburn, Virginia. ==Other websites== * Category:2004 births Category:Living people Category:American child singers Category:Musicians from Michigan Category:Singers from Michigan Category:Singers from Virginia Category:21st-century American singer- songwriters Category:Musicians from Virginia
